                            <comment id="15342348" author="michaelmior" created="Tue, 21 Jun 2016 18:09:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for clarifying. This makes a lot of sense.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15342350" author="michaelmior" created="Tue, 21 Jun 2016 18:09:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As an aside, the error message should probably change since it says &quot;partition key&quot; instead of &quot;primary key.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
